                        <MyObjectBuilder_InventoryItem>
                          <Amount>1</Amount>
                          <PhysicalContent xsi:type="MyObjectBuilder_Datapad">
                            <SubtypeName>Datapad</SubtypeName>
                            <Name>Thank You For Purchasing Baserunner</Name>
                            <Data>!!! CONGRATULATIONS !!!

Thank you for purchasing the Kharak Baserunner from the Northern COALITION.

1. Your Baserunner has been outfitted with the latest utilities, including wheels!
2. Visit Kharak's tropical Oasis and sunny deserts, and drive circles around the locals.
3. Be sure to find a ready supply of ice to extend your life and adventures.
4. Join a faction, or make a new one since you have no friends.
5. Build a station, but use small grid production because you're poor.
6. Visit the Rusty's Garage Trade Station to buy some Small Caliber Tech and make guns.
7. You are (mostly) safe in Zone 0, but your production and weapons will be very limited.
8. Visit the high desert and meet friendly neighborhood GAALSIEN pirates.
9. Raid wrecks for free loot, Zone 1 had the smallest, and Zone 3 has the most dangerous.
10. Be sure to build up your SC bank account as insurance against being wiped out.

GPS:Coalition Base:61776.43:28033.08:38602.75:#FF75C9F1:</Data>
